⚠️ Modified the Contribution:
Comment:
Wanted to make it clear that 'A' and 'Z' only appear once AT ALL in the parts (makes Shortest mode easier if you know this):
BEFORE:
There is ambiguity in the parts:
- only one starting extremity 'A',
- only one ending extremity 'Z',

AFTER:
There is ambiguity in the parts:
- only one part with an 'A',
- only one part with a 'Z',
Nice, enough complexity but not too complex, perfect for Clash of Code

This works actually pretty well.
Easy enough for a clash :P
